Description: Gets all dashboards in a Jira instance

#!/usr/bin/env node --no-warnings ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/index.js getAllDashboards

---
Name: Get Dashboard
Description: Gets a dashboard in a Jira instance
Share Tools: Get All Dashboards
Args: dashboardId: the ID of the dashboard to get

#!/usr/bin/env node --no-warnings ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/index.js getDashboard

